description: Lobsta Love is taking marvelously luscious Maine lobster through the streets of Phoenix, and the local foodies are absolutely lovin’ every bite of this selection of authentically buttery rolls stuffed to succulent perfection, as well as every other East Coast offering from this lively truck. For the tastiest urban lobster you’ll eat on the curbs, lose yourself in some Lobsta Love as soon as possible.
name: Lobsta Love
